{{Infobox pageant titleholder | name=Diana Kobzanová | birth_name= | photo= | caption= | title= Miss Czech Republic 2001 | nationalcompetition=[[Miss Universe 2002]] (Unplaced) | birth_date= {{Birth date and age|1982|3|24|mf=y}} | birth_place= [[Neuburg an der Donau|Neuburg]], [[Germany]] | measurements=90-62-92 ([[European Union|EU]]) | height={{height|m=1.80|precision=0}} | spouse= Michael Frolik | eye_color=[[Eye color#Blue|Blue]] | hair_color=[[Blond]] | children = 1 }}
'''Diana Kobzanová''' (born 24 March 1982 in [[Neuburg an der Donau|Neuburg]], [[Germany]]) is a beauty queen who won [[Miss Czech Republic]] as a 19-year-old<ref>{{cite news|url=http://revue.idnes.cz/trinacta-miss-soutezila-s-trinactkou-d83-/lidicky.aspx?c=A010403_170008_lidicky_jup|title=Třináctá Miss soutěžila s třináctkou|date=2002-09-13|publisher=revue.idnes.cz|accessdate=2015-08-29|language=Czech}}</ref> and represented her country in [[Miss Universe 2002]] in [[Puerto Rico]].
==Career==
Nowadays is Kobzanová more Czech television and radio presenter than a model. She has hosted Czech version of reality show [[Való Világ]] on [[Prima televize|TV Prima]],<ref>{{cite news|url=http://sip.denik.cz/celebrity/kobzanova_vyvoleni20070628.html|title=Noční show VyVolených ovládne Diana Kobzanová|date=2007-06-28|publisher=sip.denik.cz|accessdate=2015-08-30|language=Czech}}</ref> her own show ''Drzá Diana'' and talk show ''In-box'' on TV Óčko.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://revue.idnes.cz/kobzanova-se-vraci-do-televize-od-unora-posiluje-ocko-pdn-/missamodelky.aspx?c=A090203_143249_missamodelky_ved|title=Kobzanová se vrací do televize, od února posiluje Óčko|date=2009-02-03|publisher=revue.idnes.cz|accessdate=2015-08-30|language=Czech}}</ref><ref>[http://ocko.tv/profil-moderatora/diana-kobzanova-58750032.html Profile] at TV Óčko website</ref> She also hosted reality show about home decor ''Vrabci v hrsti'' and show ''Horký prachy''.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.chytrazena.cz/divoky-zabavny-a-originalni-porad-o-bytovem-designu-to-jsou-vrabci-v-hrsti-15859.html|title=Divoký, zábavný a originální pořad o bytovém designu - to jsou Vrabci v hrsti|date=2011-08-16|publisher=chytrazena.cz|accessdate=2015-09-20|language=Czech}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.investicniweb.cz/zpravy/2011/6/7/horky-prachy-zabavny-edukativni-porad-o-investovani-startuje-tuto-nedeli-na-prime/|title=Horký prachy: Zábavný a edukativní pořad o investování startuje tuto neděli na Primě!|date=2011-06-07|publisher=investicniweb.cz|accessdate=2015-09-20|language=Czech}}</ref> At radio Frekvence 1 she presented programmes ''Na titulní straně'', ''Styl'' and ''Sportbar''. She was on air for more than 8 years.<ref>[http://www.frekvence1.cz/radio/moderatori/diana-kobzanova-7.html Profile] at Frekvence 1 website</ref>
==Personal life== Kobzanová was four years in a relationship with [[footballer]] [[Martin Jiránek]]. Then with businessman Tomáš Petera and [[Rallying|rally]] driver [[Štěpán Vojtěch]] for more than three years. Nowadays Kobzanová is in a relationship with [[ice hockey]] player [[Michael Frolík]].<ref>{{cite news|url=http://prask.nova.cz/clanek/novinky/kobzanova-ma-noveho-chlapa-podivejte-se-koho-uz-mela-v-posteli.html|title=Kobzanová má nového chlapa. Podívejte se, koho už měla v posteli!|date=2013-06-25|publisher=prask.nova.cz|accessdate=2015-08-30|language=Czech}}</ref>
In December 2014 she gave birth to a daughter Ella.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://prask.nova.cz/clanek/novinky/diana-kobzanova-tajne-porodila-holcicce-dala-krasne-jmeno.html|title=Diana Kobzanová tajně porodila. Holčičce dala krásné jméno|date=2014-12-20|publisher=prask.nova.cz|accessdate=2015-08-30|language=Czech}}</ref>
==Naked pictures== Few months after her victory she posed for Czech pornographic magazine LEO for 5 million Czech crowns, the equivalent of around 207,320 US dollars. As a result, she lost her title and faced a lawsuit by chairman Miloslav Zapletal who claimed she had damaged the competition's good name. After 4 years of lawsuit, she won and didn't need to apologize publicly or pay a penalty.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.radio.cz/en/section/curraffrs/former-miss-and-one-off-centrefold-wins-her-day-in-court|title=Former Miss - and one-off centrefold - wins her day in court|date=2005-08-23|publisher=radio.cz|accessdate=2015-08-31}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://revue.idnes.cz/kobzanova-nemusi-zapletalovi-platit-za-porno-fou-/lidicky.aspx?c=A060620_103811_lidicky_lf|title=Kobzanová nemusí Zapletalovi platit za porno|date=2006-07-20|publisher=revue.idnes.cz|accessdate=2015-08-31|language=Czech}}</ref>
